info.title: Nota Fiscal â€“ Create, Update
info.description: This service is based on the OData and can be consumed in Brazilian integration scenarios. To create a nota fiscal document, enter the nota fiscal data - the system generates the nota fiscal and returns the document number. To update a nota fiscal document, enter the document number and the data to be changed - the system updates the nota fiscal accordingly.

x-sap-shortText: Create and update notas fiscais using this inbound and synchronous service for Brazil

post.summary: Creates or updates a nota fiscal.
post.description: Creates or updates a nota fiscal using deep insert requests. This means that consumers can create a nota fiscal with all possible sub-entities (for example, partners or items). To update a nota fiscal, consumers must fill in the document number in the request.
